Class Vector2d

  • java.lang.Object
    • net.edzard.kinetic.Vector2d

    public class Vector2d
extends java.lang.Object
implements java.io.Serializable
    Stores a two-dimensional value. Used for positions and sizes (horizontal and vertical extents).
